outputs.output_descr: Strengthen focus on improved cross-sectoral governance for sound management of chemicals (SMC) at the national and local levels and establish stronger SMC links with national development planning priorities,  processes and plans to achieve the MDGs.

project_descr: Kyrgyzstan, UNDP and UNEP partnership initiative for the integration of sound man-agement of chemicals considerations into development plans and processes.
project_title: MAINSTREAMING OF SOUND MANAGEMENT OF CHEMICALS
